  m_Name: tuna (school)
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::FishData
  <fishName>k__BackingField: Tuna
  <fishFact>k__BackingField: "Tuna are warm-blooded \u2014 one of the very few fish
    that can regulate their body temperature, which lets them swim in cold, deep
    water and recover speed quickly. A school of bluefin tuna is an awe-inspiring
    sight: hundreds of torpedo-shaped bodies moving in perfect synchrony at speeds
    that rival boats. They migrate thousands of kilometers across entire ocean basins
    every year."
